{"tid":2478250,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】當BLACKPINK&Red Velvet融合在TWICE身上！韓網民：毫無破綻，雞皮疙瘩都出來了","createTime":"2021-04-07T02:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T03:04:39.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"194407c27d363942ee9797dea263b9371b7d6b57","tid":2478250,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_c21be1fe7ef1b32e0d3563768b0cf40c/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-06/134699-902356.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_c21be1fe7ef1b32e0d3563768b0cf40c%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-06%2F134699-902356.jpg&h=2602e0c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當BLACKPINK和Red Velvet遇上了TWICE會產生怎樣的化學反應？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_ffca7c71363e37c48d69901acdfa0e85/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-06/134698-902325.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_ffca7c71363e37c48d69901acdfa0e85%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-06%2F134698-902325.png&h=9eeba6f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IG@blackpinkcofficial<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_459884e64c54306964819bd95427eb14/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-06/134699-902354.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_459884e64c54306964819bd95427eb14%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-06%2F134699-902354.png&h=79b14d9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IG@redvelvet.smtown<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_fb78cc864facdaa60078b856e584009c/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-04-06/134699-902332.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_fb78cc864facdaa60078b856e584009c%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-04-06%2F134699-902332.jpg&h=c32a8c69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IG@official.twice<br />\n<br />\n換臉APP被用在了女團的身上，YouTube上有博主公開了一則TWICE歌曲《Fancy》的影片，9名成員一一亮相，只是影片看到一半時不少人都發現，嗯？ 她們似乎不是我們認識的TWICE啊，怎麼隱隱有了其他人的影子？ 原來是博主利用了DEEP FAKES把BLACKPINK和Red Velvet成員們的臉「安」在了TWICE的身上，不仔細看差點都沒看出任何破綻，只能說黑科技太可怕了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7Gbe2I1uXmc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7Gbe2I1uXmc&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtIHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=61a9aa75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7Gbe2I1uXmc</a><br />\n<br />\n大家都看出來了嗎？<br />\n娜璉-Jennie<br />\n定延-Jisoo<br />\nMOMO-Lisa<br />\nSANA-ROSE<br />\n志效-Wendy<br />\nMINA-澀琪<br />\n多賢-Yeri<br />\n彩瑛-Irene<br />\n子瑜-Joy<br />\n<br />\n看到這則影片，不少粉絲和網友也都紛紛留言表達了自己的意見，稱：「雞皮疙瘩都出來了」、「希望換臉技術不要用在犯罪上」、「 第一次看的時候都沒發現人不一樣，以為都是TWICE」、「真的太逼真了，千萬不能被有心之人拿來犯罪」、「 太可怕了，起了一身的雞皮疙瘩」等。<br />\n<br />\n「圖：YouTube@K-Chillex LUVedit、IG@redvelvet.smtown、blackpinkcofficial、@official.twice」"},{"pid":"d5d14c6f9d4e2a96ca90f7aea89d7c88fbbeefe7","tid":2478250,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:14:24.000Z","msg":"痴線...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ac915147856a9b8df3b6efbfb26c94ad8d405f","tid":2478250,"uid":174654,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:16:39.000Z","msg":"irene個樣key落彩瑛到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣處刑牙彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb678fa25a2dab7e081abfc075d0c108cb667e7","tid":2478250,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3ac915147856a9b8df3b6efbfb26c94ad8d405f","tid":2478250,"uid":174654,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:16:39.000Z","msg":"irene個樣key落彩瑛到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣處刑牙彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:20:40.000Z","msg":"西女人不配<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgm